Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}P... P...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Passed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She has passed out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What? What happened?\N--Sugar has passed out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this some kind of joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The servants that we've been \Ncollecting for a decade
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nare turning back into humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spell of the Hobby-Hobby \NFruit is being removed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tontattas' operation must've\Nbeen pulled off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you\NUsopp would take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, look at the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've turned back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Honey!\N--I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is happening here?!\NThe toys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The toys are turning into humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Sugar has...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A decade of our hard work...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar must've been beaten\Nby somebody-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic that shitty little tramp is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I hope she's not hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy!\NYou said such an unkind thing but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you actually care about her!\NSo hard-boiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...\N--{\i1}Palace, please answer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We keep getting emergency reports!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is an emergency call\Nfrom Sevio in the south!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The toys working at the port\Nsuddenly turned into pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...\N--{\i1}This is Carta in the east!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The toys turned into old Dressrosa soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They turned into gov't officials!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy soldiers and\Nsenior officials from abroad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild animals! This is Primula District!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've turned back into a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stay with me, Usopp!\N--Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and everybody else, we all turned \Nback into humans thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Usoland!\N--Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Operation SOP has been accomplished!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody turned back into a human\Nand they're all happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Onepoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Mom, Onepoko is acting strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Onepoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One...poko? One...poko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One... No! My darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've turned back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad! You're not Onepoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, I'm your dad!\N--Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:13:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have we forgotten about you\Nall this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how the spell worked!\NI thought I was gonna live as a toy forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey Dad! Can you lift me up high?!\N--Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! You're quiet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go, stone guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp... Little People...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Operation Sugar Oversurprised \Nand Panic went...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...{\i1}super{\i0} well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Usopp, stay with me!\N--Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think... I can't... carry on...\Nanymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland! Please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't die!\N--I don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland has died!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usolan...d?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hero's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland! Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything... went as planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest... to my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle has...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:15:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Onepoko, the dog you've \Nbeen pushing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just carry it, Onepoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you boss me around...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Like I was your slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can forgive everyone else but you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Palace! Send some backup ASAP!\NThe pirates are out of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not enough yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat the hell out of Doflamingo's men!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's wrong?! Answer me! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you treat me so violently?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Esta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh yeah!\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I have a boyfriend!\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cheated on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I forgot about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was forgotten for a decade!\NI hate Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take down Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were fooled by Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NHe's a good king.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't know who he really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out, Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta pay you back\N10 years' worth of pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Issho-{\i1}san{\i0}, what is happening here-{\i1}dara{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the tides have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:18:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness of this country must be\Nmuch deeper than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness-{\i1}dara{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kill Doflamingo's men!\N--Let them all shed their blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take our country back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring down Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those pieces of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soldier-san is a brave man{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He will always be by your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soldier-san is a brave man{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He will always be by your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had been forgetting everything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Kyros! King Riku-sama!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kyros?\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. It doesn't ring a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, I remember clearly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I lost my memories of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!\NWhat do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where did the soldier go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's him.\N--Huh? That's a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The toys were originally humans
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they were erased from our memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Devil Fruit eater Sugar\Npassed out now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we got our memories back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the former commander of\Nthe King Riku Army - Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest gladiator\Nin the history of the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the old man the statue is of!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rebecca's biological father!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! She said she didn't know him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When people forget about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing you can do\Nto make them remember you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he's just been watching over \Nhis beloved daughter for a decade!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.47,0:22:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has always been by her side, \Nday after day, as a toy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.11,0:22:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Kyros, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.53,0:22:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to keep you waiting\Nfor a decade!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm here to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.08,0:23:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to take back the real Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.02,0:23:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kyros takes down Doflamingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This sends unprecedented shock \Nwaves throughout the Royal Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:33.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and at the same time, the fight \Nat the Colosseum is about to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:35.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,reach its dramatic climax!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The battle for the Flare-Flare Fruit\Nfinally comes to an end!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Fire Fist Strikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.67,0:23:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flare-Flare Fruit Power Returns!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
